name: 李老师不是你老师
content: According to a netizen’s contribution, Nanning Huibo Parking Service Co., Ltd. issued an internal notice requiring employees to refrain from posting inappropriate comments and pictures on the Internet, external websites, social platforms, etc. According to the contributor’s description, Nanning Huibo Parking Lot previously caused public opinion due to the sky-high charges, resulting in a large number of local people collectively refusing to pay fines. Subsequently, Huibo announced that it had reached a cooperation with the local court and would recover the maliciously overdue fines, which once again attracted public attention. On May 18, the Nanning government issued an announcement that it would improve the problems in its work.
